translated: Dahl, Per E., lieutenant colonel, Växjö, b. 2/10/90 in Mora, Kopparb. County, son of mining commissioner Ehs D. and Maria Pettersson. Married on 26th with Clara Waldemarsson. Children: Olof b. 27, Margaretha 28, Lena 32. Graduated from Mog:ex. in Västerås in 09, officer training in 11, SS 16 and 35, AIHS 17, flight training education in 20, KHS 23, signed off as lieutenant colonel in Kuris in 25. Served as second lieutenant in v. I. 28 11, (lieutenant there in 16, captain in 26, major in v. I. 19 36, v. I. 11 40, lieutenant colonel there in 42, enrolled as chief of staff in 11 42-46, retired in 46, appointed as representative of S. Sv :es’ Trä-varuexp ifören. in Växjö since 46. Member of StadsfuMm. and kyrkofuiilm. in Sollefteå city 34-36, chairman of 1. 21 ’skyttefören. 33-36, in 1. 19 ditto 38-40, in I. 11 ditto 41-45 and in Växjö skyttekrets 43-46. Hobby: rifle shooting. RSO 32, Svsfb förtj:SM 42, Crown Property's Gold Medal, Väster-norrl's skytteförb. förtj:SM, Norrb. Sikytteförb. förtj:SM, Highest year medal in gold (rifle), Master's medal in gold (rifle), Swimming medal in gold, Skiing medal in gold.
